    {
      "id": "walkthroughs-readiness-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Status",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 1490,
        "y": -410
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Status\n\n**Have walkthroughs (and demo graphs):**\n- Views (authoring + consumption)\n- Script (authoring + result routing)\n- Bridge (import/export + allowlists + runtime grants + discovery)\n- Legend + Type Definitions (deterministic legend + spawnable node classes)\n- Port + Reference (preview/navigate modes, deterministic view list, minimap fallback)\n- Declaration (identity/dependencies/authority/surfaces)\n- GitHub (sign-in, installation, commit, github:// load)\n- Edge Class (authoring/export/import/consume) *(in progress / still tightening)*\n\n**Need walkthroughs:**\n- Canvas view payloads (authoring + rendering)\n\n**Likely soon:**\n- Plugin node basics (extension surfaces, safety, discovery)\n\nDefinition of done for each walkthrough:\n- Author the primitive\n- Render it on-canvas\n- Edit it via drawer (hydrated)\n- Consume/discover it (ports/legend/etc)\n- Export/import if applicable",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1777435860067,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
    },
